<section>
  <h2 style="margin-bottom: 10px;">The Rise of the Professions Shapes Progressivism</h2>

  <p style="font-size:1.02em; max-width: 900px; line-height:1.25; margin: 0 auto 14px auto;">
    Professionalization does not just create jobs. It creates a way of thinking that values expertise, standards,
